#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gametype:"
msgstr "Vrsta igre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logic, Arcade"
msgstr "Logika, Arkadna"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>One</para>"
msgstr "<para>Eden</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kblocks; is the classic falling blocks game. The idea is stack the falling "
"blocks in a way that lines are completely filled. When a line is completed "
"it is removed, and more space is available in the play area. When there is "
"not enough space for blocks to fall, the game is over."
msgstr ""
"&kblocks; je klasična igra padajočih blokov. Ideja je zložiti padajoče bloke "
"tako, da so črte popolnoma zapolnjene. Ko je linija končana, se odstrani in "
"v igralnem prostoru je na voljo več prostora. Ko ni dovolj prostora za "
"padanje blokov, je igre konec."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kblocks; gameboard"
msgstr "&kblocks; igralna plošča"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rotate the falling blocks, and fit them together to complete lines and clear "
"the playfield."
msgstr ""
"Zavrtite padajoče bloke in jih sestavite skupaj, da dokončate linije in "
"očistite igrišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, falling blocks can be moved left or right using the &Left; or "
"&Right; arrow keys. The &Down; arrow key makes the block drop faster, and "
"the &Up; arrow key is used to rotate the block. The keys used for each game "
"action can be configured in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto lahko padajoče bloke premaknete levo ali desno s smernima tipkama "
"&Left; ali &Right;. Puščica &Down; dol pospeši padec bloka, puščica &Up; se "
"uporablja za vrtenje bloka. Tipke, ki se uporabljajo za posamezno dejanje "
"igre, je mogoče konfigurirati v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "The rules are simple: just keep space for the blocks to fall!"
msgstr "Pravila so preprosta: samo imejte prostor, da bloki lahko padejo!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a new block cannot fall, the game is over."
msgstr "Ko nov blok ne more več pasti, je igre konec."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not forget to check the preview area: it shows the next piece that will "
"be released."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite preveriti območja predogleda: prikazuje naslednji del, ki bo "
"izdan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "For additional points, try to remove several lines at once."
msgstr "Za dodatne točke poskusite odstraniti več vrstic hkrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commands/Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Ukazi/Bližnjice na tipkovnici"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following sections briefly describe each menubar option."
msgstr "Naslednji razdelki na kratko opisujejo vsako možnost menijske vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Single Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ena igra</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new single player game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro za enega igralca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Human vs AI</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Človek proti umetni inteligenci</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare your skills with the AI and play against the computer using the same "
"sequence of falling blocks, where you have the first turn."
msgstr ""
"Primerjajte svoje spretnosti z umetno inteligenco in igrajte proti "
"računalniku z uporabo istega zaporedja padajočih blokov, kjer ste prvi na "
"vrsti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pauses the game."
msgstr "Začasno ustavi igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows you the high score (the maximum number of points) for each "
"difficulty level."
msgstr ""
"To vam pokaže visoko oceno (največje število točk) za vsako težavnostno "
"stopnjo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kblocks;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kblocks;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lets you set the difficulty level from a sub-menu."
msgstr "Omogoča nastavitev težavnostne stopnje iz podmenija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are three default levels of difficulty: <guimenuitem>Easy</"
"guimenuitem> (game starts at level 0), <guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem> "
"(starts at level 5), and <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem> (starts at level "
"10)."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo tri privzete stopnje težavnosti: <guimenuitem>Enostavna</"
"guimenuitem> (igra se začne na stopnji 0), <guimenuitem>Srednja</"
"guimenuitem> (začne se na 5. stopnji) in <guimenuitem>Težka</guimenuitem> "
"(začne se na stopnji 10)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kblocks; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kblocks; ima skupno s &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

