#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These shortcuts can be changed by selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from "
"the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Te bližnjice lahko spremenite tako, da izberete <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change the way the game looks?"
msgstr "Ali lahko spremenim videz igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, click on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kblocks;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Da, kliknite na menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kblocks;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game settings can be configured by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kblocks;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menubar. A dialog will appear."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve igre lahko konfigurirate tako, da v menijski vrstici izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kblocks;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže se pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati novo temo, preprosto izberite temo na izbirnem seznamu. "
"Vsak element na seznamu prikazuje majhen predogled levo od imena teme. Izbor "
"se takoj uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> button, located at the bottom part of this "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste zadovoljni z izbrano temo, lahko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Zapri</"
"guibutton>, ki se nahaja na dnu tega pogovornega okna."

